title: A Titan-ing Division
description:
Mina and Nora Princiotti of The Ringer discuss the punishments levied against Stephen Ross, the Dolphins, and Deshaun Watson. Then they preview what to expect from the teams in the AFC South- Jaguars (28:35), Titans (44:34), Texans (56:47), and Colts (1:08:13).
